1 AN ACT relating to the State Fair Board.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 247.210 is amended to read as follows:
4 No member of the State Fair Board or any official of any department shall be an exhibitor
